         <abstract id="aspace_0b560a3798de83cd0cbb8b168cb2d06b">The papers consist of writings and research materials dealing with Russian history, particularly the Romanov dynasty, Rasputin, and the origins of the Russian Revolution. Also included are materials on Peter the Great and the Jews in the Russian revolutionary movement. </abstract>
         <langmaterial id="aspace_c32f43e92e7a67292f5cdfca13d8a0d4">
            <language>The materials are primarily in Russian, with some items in French and English. </language>
         </langmaterial>
